                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import pulp as pp
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #linprog
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                c=np.array([2,3,-5])              
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                A=np.array([[2,-5,1],[-1,-3,-1]])  #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                b=np.array([10,-12])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Aeq=np.array([[1,1,1]])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                beq=np.array([7])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #str
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                m=pp.LpProblem(str,sense=pp.LpMaximize)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #catIntegerBinary01
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x=[pp.LpVariable(f'x{i}',lowBound=0,cat='Continuous') for i in [1,2,3]]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                m+=pp.lpDot(c,x)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #for
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in range (len(A)):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    m+=(pp.lpDot(A[i],x)>=b[i])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #for
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in range (len(Aeq)):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    m+=(pp.lpDot(Aeq[i],x)==beq[i])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #solve
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                m.solve()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(pp.value(m.objective))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #x
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print([pp.value(var) for var in x])

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                c=np.array([-6,3,-1,0,0,0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Aeq=np.array([[2,1,0,1,0,0],[-4,-2,3,0,1,0],[1,-2,1,0,0,1]])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                beq=np.array([8,14,18])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x1=(0,None)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x3=(0,None)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                res=so.linprog(c,A_eq=Aeq,b_eq=beq,bounds=(x1,x2,x3,x4,x5,x6))

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def func(x):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return x[0]**2+x[1]**2+x[2]**2+8
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                cons=({'type':'ineq','fun':lambda x:x[0]**2-x[1]+x[2]**2},
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      {'type':'ineq','fun':lambda x:-x[0]-x[1]-x[2]**2+20},
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      {'type':'eq','fun':lambda x:-x[0]-x[1]**2+2},
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      {'type':'eq','fun':lambda x:x[1]+2*x[2]**2-3})
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                bounds=[[0,None],[0,None],[0,None]]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x0=np.array([0,0,0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                res=so.minimize(func,x0,bounds=bounds,constraints=cons)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(res)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.optimize import minimize
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def rosen(x):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """The Rosenbrock function"""
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return sum(100.0*(x[1:]-x[:-1]**2.0)**2.0 + (1-x[:-1])**2.0)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #rosen_der
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def rosen_der(x):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    xm = x[1:-1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    xm_m1 = x[:-2]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    xm_p1 = x[2:]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    der = np.zeros_like(x)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    der[1:-1] = 200*(xm-xm_m1**2) - 400*(xm_p1 - xm**2)*xm - 2*(1-xm)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    der[0] = -400*x[0]*(x[1]-x[0]**2) - 2*(1-x[0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    der[-1] = 200*(x[-1]-x[-2]**2)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return der
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def rosen_hess(x):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x = np.asarray(x)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    H = np.diag(-400*x[:-1],1) - np.diag(400*x[:-1],-1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    diagonal = np.zeros_like(x)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    diagonal[0] = 1200*x[0]**2-400*x[1]+2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    diagonal[-1] = 200
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    diagonal[1:-1] = 202 + 1200*x[1:-1]**2 - 400*x[2:]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    H = H + np.diag(diagonal)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return H
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.optimize import Bounds
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #Bounds:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                bounds = Bounds([0, -0.5], [1.0, 2.0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ineq_cons = {'type': 'ineq',
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             'fun' : lambda x: np.array([1 - x[0] - 2*x[1],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         1 - x[0]**2 - x[1],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         1 - x[0]**2 + x[1]]),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             #jacfun
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             'jac' : lambda x: np.array([[-1.0, -2.0],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         [-2*x[0], -1.0],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         [-2*x[0], 1.0]])}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                eq_cons = {'type': 'eq',
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           'fun' : lambda x: np.array([2*x[0] + x[1] - 1]),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           'jac' : lambda x: np.array([2.0, 1.0])}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x0 = np.array([0.5, 0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                res = minimize(rosen, x0, method='SLSQP', jac=rosen_der,constraints=[eq_cons, ineq_cons], options={'ftol': 1e-9, 'disp': True},bounds=bounds)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(res.x)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                model:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                sets:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                row/1..4/:b;
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                col/1..5/:c1,c2,x;
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                link(row,col):a;
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                endsets
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                data:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                c1=1,1,3,4,2;
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                c2=-8,-2,-3,-1,-2;
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                a=1 1 1 1 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                1 2 2 1 6
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                2 1 6 0 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                0 0 1 1 5;
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                b=400,800,200,200;
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                enddata
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                max=@sum(col:c1*x^2+c2*x);
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                @for(row(i):@sum(col(j):a(i,j)*x(j))<b(i));
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                @for(col:@gin(x));
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                @for(col:@bnd(0,x,99));
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                end

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pulp.LpProblem

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xxxxxxxxxx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #pprint
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from pprint import pprint
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def TransProblem(costs,x_max,y_max):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    prob=pp.LpProblem("TransProblem",sense=pp.LpMaximize)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    var=[[pp.LpVariable(f'x{i}{j}',lowBound=0,cat='Integer')for j in range(len(costs[0]))] for i in range (len(costs))]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    #var
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    flatten=lambda x:[y for l in x for y in flatten(l)] if type(x) is list else [x]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    prob+=pp.lpDot(flatten(var),costs.flatten())
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for i in range(len(costs)):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        prob+=(pp.lpSum(var[i])<=x_max[i])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for j in range(len(costs[0])):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        prob+=(pp.lpSum([var[i][j] for i in range(len(costs))])<=y_max[j])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    prob.solve()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return {'objective':pp.value(prob.objective),'var':[[pp.value(var[i][j]) for j in range(len(costs[0]))] for i in range (len(costs))]}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if __name__ == '__main__':
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    costs=np.array([[500,550,630,1000,800,700],[800,700,600,950,900,930],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [1000,960,840,650,600,700],[1200,1040,980,860,880,780]])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    max_plant=np.array([76,88,96,40])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    max_cultivation=np.array([42,56,44,39,60,59])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    res=TransProblem(costs,max_plant,max_cultivation)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(res['objective'])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    pprint(res['var'])

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ABBABAz*z2, Az*z1, Bz2z1z*

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pulp()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xxxxxxxxxx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import pulp as pp
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                c=np.array([3,4,1])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                A=np.array([[1,6,2],[2,0,0]])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                b=np.array([5,3])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                m=pp.LpProblem(sense=pp.LpMinimize)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x=[pp.LpVariable(f'x{i}',lowBound=0,cat='Integer') for i in [1,2,3]]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                m+=pp.lpDot(c,x)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in range (len(A)):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    m+=(pp.lpDot(A[i],x)>=b[i])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                m.solve()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(pp.value(m.objective))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print([pp.value(var) for var in x])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                scipy
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xxxxxxxxxx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import math
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import scipy.optimize as so
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import sys
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def IntProblem(c, A, b, Aeq, beq, t=1.0E-8):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    res = so.linprog(c, A_ub=A, b_ub=b, A_eq=Aeq, b_eq=beq)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    bestVal = sys.maxsize
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    bestX = res.x
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if not(type(res.x) is float or res.status != 0):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        bestVal = sum([x*y for x,y in zip(c, bestX)])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if all(((x-math.floor(x))<=t or (math.ceil(x)-x)<=t) for x in bestX):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        return (bestVal,bestX)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    else:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        ind = [i for i, x in enumerate(bestX) if (x-math.floor(x))>t and (math.ceil(x)-x)>t][0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newCon1 = [0]*len(A[0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newCon2 = [0]*len(A[0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newCon1[ind] = -1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newCon2[ind] = 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newA1 = A.copy()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newA2 = A.copy()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newA1.append(newCon1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newA2.append(newCon2)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newB1 = b.copy()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newB2 = b.copy()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newB1.append(-math.ceil(bestX[ind]))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        newB2.append(math.floor(bestX[ind]))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        r1 = IntProblem(c, newA1, newB1, Aeq, beq)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        r2 = IntProblem(c, newA2, newB2, Aeq, beq)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if r1[0] < r2[0]:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return r1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        else:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return r2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                c = [3,4,1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                A = [[-1,-6,-2],[-2,0,0]]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                b = [-5,-3]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Aeq = [[0,0,0]]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                beq = [0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(IntProblem(c, A, b, Aeq, beq))

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def second():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    face_num = 1000
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    t = np.random.random(size=face_num) * 2 * np.pi - np.pi  #-pipi
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x = np.cos(t)   #x-1~1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y = np.sin(t)   #y-1~1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    z = np.zeros(t.shape)  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    zr = np.zeros(t.shape)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    i_set = np.arange(0,face_num,1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for i in i_set:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        len = np.sqrt(np.random.random())
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        x[i] = x[i] * len
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        y[i] = y[i] * len
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        z[i] = np.exp(np.square(x[i])+np.square(y[i]))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        zr[i] = np.random.random(1) * 3
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    fig = plt.figure()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax = Axes3D(fig)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.scatter(x,y,z,c = 'r', marker = '.')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.scatter(x,y,zr,c = 'b', marker = '.')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    _t = np.arange(0,7,0.1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    _x = np.cos(_t)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    _y = np.sin(_t)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.plot(_x,_y,'g-')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.scatter(_x,_y,3,c = 'g', marker = '.')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.xlim(-1.1,1.1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.ylim(-1.1,1.1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.xlabel('x')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.ylabel('y')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.title('Random Scatter')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    n = 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for i in range(face_num):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if zr[i]<z[i]:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            n +=1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ratio = n/face_num
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v = 3 * np.pi
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    value = ratio * v
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(ratio, value)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.show()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return value

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.integrate import odeint    #  scipy.integrate 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def pray(W,t):  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x_1,x_2= W  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dx1_dt = x_1*(1-0.1*x_2) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dx2_dt = x_2*(-0.5+0.02*x_1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.array([dx1_dt,dx2_dt])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                t = np.arange(0, 30, 0.01)  #  (start,stop,step)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                W1 = (25,2)  #  W1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                track1 = odeint(pray, W1, t)  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fig = plt.figure()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax=fig.add_subplot(111)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.plot(t, track1[:,1], color='magenta')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.plot(t, track1[:,0], color='orange') 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.set_title("Prey System")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                scipy.integrate.odeint(func, y0, t, args=())

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • funccallable(y, t, ) f ( y , t ) y t

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • y0array y0 y0

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • t: arrayy0t0

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • argfunc

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • yarray (len(t),len(y0)) t y
