                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 2. (scipy.integrate.odeint)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.integrate import odeint    #  scipy.integrate 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ,  W=[x,y,z]  dW/dt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def lorenz(W,t,p,r,b):  # by youcans
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x, y, z = W  # W=[x,y,z]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dx_dt = p*(y-x)  # dx/dt = p*(y-x), p: sigma
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dy_dt = x*(r-z) - y  # dy/dt = x*(r-z)-y, r:rho
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dz_dt = x*y - b*z  # dz/dt = x*y - b*z, b;beta
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.array([dx_dt,dy_dt,dz_dt])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                t = np.arange(0, 30, 0.01)  #  (start,stop,step)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                paras = (10.0, 28.0, 3.0)  #  Lorenz  (p,r,b)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # odeintlorenz,  W1W2 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                W1 = (0.0, 1.00, 0.0)  #  W1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                track1 = odeint(lorenz, W1, t, args=(10.0, 28.0, 3.0))  # args 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                W2 = (0.0, 1.01, 0.0)  #  W2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                track2 = odeint(lorenz, W2, t, args=paras)  #  paras 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fig = plt.figure()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax=fig.add_subplot(111,projection='3d')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.plot(track1[:,0], track1[:,1], track1[:,2], color='magenta') #  1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.plot(track2[:,0], track2[:,1], track2[:,2], color='deepskyblue') #  2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.set_title("Lorenz attractor by scipy.integrate.odeint")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.integrate import odeint  #  scipy.integrate 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  Y=[u,v]  dY/dt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def deriv(Y, t, a, w):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    u, v = Y  # Y=[u,v]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dY_dt = [v, -2*a*v-w*w*u]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return dY_dt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                t = np.arange(0, 20, 0.01)  #  (start,stop,step)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  (a, w)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                paras1 = (1, 0.6)  # a^2 - w^2 > 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                paras2 = (1, 1)  # a^2 - w^2 = 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                paras3 = (0.3, 1)  # a^2 - w^2 < 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ode,  W1W2 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Y0 = (1.0, 0.0)  #  Y0=[u0,v0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Y1 = odeint(deriv, Y0, t, args=paras1)  # args 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Y2 = odeint(deriv, Y0, t, args=paras2)  # args 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Y3 = odeint(deriv, Y0, t, args=paras3)  # args 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # W2 = (0.0, 1.01, 0.0)  #  W2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # track2 = odeint(lorenz, W2, t, args=paras)  #  paras 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(t, Y1[:, 0], 'r-', label='u1(t)')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(t, Y2[:, 0], 'b-', label='u2(t)')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(t, Y3[:, 0], 'g-', label='u3(t)')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(t, Y1[:, 1], 'r:', label='v1(t)')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(t, Y2[:, 1], 'b:', label='v2(t)')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(t, Y3[:, 1], 'g:', label='v3(t)')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.axis([0, 20, -0.8, 1.2])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.legend(loc='best')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.title("Second ODE by scipy.integrate.odeint")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                BVP

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                scipy.integrate.solve_bvp()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                scipy.integrate.solve_bvp(fun, bc, x, y, p=None)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • funccallable fun(x, y, ) f ( y , x )y x p

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • bccallable bc(ya, yb, ) y p

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • x: arrayshape (m,) xaxb

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • y: arrayshape (n,m) i x[i]

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • p: array func bc

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • sol: PPoly PPoly y

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • x: array (m,)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • y: array (n,m) y

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • yp: array (n,m) y 

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xxxxxxxxxx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.integrate import odeint, solve_bvp
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 1. DEMO
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # y'' + abs(y) = 0, y(0)=0.5, y(4)=-1.5
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  dY/dx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def dydx(x, y):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dy0 = y[1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dy1 = -abs(y[0])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.vstack((dy0, dy1))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def boundCond(ya, yb):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    fa = 0.5  #  y(xa=0) = 0.5
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    fb = -1.5  #  y(xb=4) = -1.5
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.array([ya[0]-fa,yb[0]-fb])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xa, xb = 0, 4  #  (xa,xb)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # fa, fb = 0.5, -1.5  #  y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xini = np.linspace(xa, xb, 11)  #  x 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                yini = np.zeros((2, xini.size))  #  y (y0y1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                res = solve_bvp(dydx, boundCond, xini, yini)  #  BVP
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xSol = np.linspace(xa, xb, 100)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ySol = res.sol(xSol)[0]  #  y 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(xSol, ySol, label='y')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # plt.legend()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.xlabel("x")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.ylabel("y")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.title("scipy.integrate.solve_bvp")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.integrate import odeint, solve_bvp
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 3. 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  h=[h0,h1]  dh/dx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def dhdx(x,h):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    #  dh0/dx, dh1/dx 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dh0 = h[1]  #  dh0/dx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dh1 = (h[0]-1)*(1+h[1]*h[1])**1.5  #  dh1/dx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.vstack((dh0, dh1))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def boundCond(ha,hb):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # ha = 0  # h0(x=-1) = 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # hb = 0  # h0(x=1) = 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.array([ha[0],hb[0]])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xa, xb = -1, 1  #  (xa=0, xb=1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xini = np.linspace(xa, xb, 11)  #  x 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                hini = np.zeros((2, xini.size))  #  h 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                res = solve_bvp(dhdx, boundCond, xini, hini)   #  BVP
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # scipy.integrate.solve_bvp(fun, bc, x, y,..)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #   fun(x, y, ..),  f(y,x)y x 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #   bc(ya, yb, ..), y 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #   x: shape (m) xaxb
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #   y: shape (n,m) i  x[i]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xSol = np.linspace(xa, xb, 100)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                hSol = res.sol(xSol)[0]  #  h 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(xSol, hSol, label='h(x)')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.xlabel("x")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.ylabel("h(x)")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.axis([-1, 1, 0, 1])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.title("Cross section of water drop by BVP xupt")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xxxxxxxxxx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.integrate import odeint, solve_bvp
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 4. Mathieu 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # y0' = y1, y1' = -(lam-2*q*cos(2x))y0)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # y0(0)=1, y1(0)=0, y1(pi)=0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  dY/dx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def dydx(x, y, p): # p 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    lam = p[0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    q = 10
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dy0 = y[1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dy1 = -(lam-2*q*np.cos(2*x))*y[0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.vstack((dy0, dy1))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def boundCond(ya, yb, p):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    lam = p[0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return np.array([ya[0]-1,ya[0],yb[0]])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xa, xb = 0, np.pi  #  (xa,xb)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xini = np.linspace(xa, xb, 11)  #  x 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xSol = np.linspace(xa, xb, 100)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for k in range(5):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    A = 0.75*k
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y0ini = np.cos(8*xini)  #  y0 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y1ini = -A*np.sin(8*xini)  #  y1 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yini = np.vstack((y0ini, y1ini))  #  y=[y0,y1] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    res = solve_bvp(dydx, boundCond, xini, yini, p=[10])  #  BVP
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y0 = res.sol(xSol)[0]  #  y 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y1 = res.sol(xSol)[1]  #  y 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.plot(xSol, y0, '--')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.plot(xSol, y1,'-',label='A = {:.2f}'.format(A))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.xlabel("xupt")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.ylabel("y")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.title("Characteristic function of Mathieu equation")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.axis([0, np.pi, -5, 5])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.legend(loc='best')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.text(2,-4,"youcans-xupt",color='whitesmoke')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from heapq import *
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from collections import defaultdict
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                inf=sys.maxsize
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def Dijkstra(edges,from_node,to_node):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    go_path=[]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    to_node=to_node-1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    g=defaultdict(list)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for l,r,c in edges:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        g[l].append((c,r))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    q,seen=[(0,from_node-1,())],set()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    cost,v1,path=0,0,0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    while q:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        (cost,v1,path)=heappop(q)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if v1 not in seen:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            seen.add(v1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            path=(v1,path)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            if(v1==to_node):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                break
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            for c,v2 in g.get(v1,()):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if v2 not in seen:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    heappush(q,(cost+c,v2,path))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if v1!=to_node:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        return float('inf'),[]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if len(path)>0:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        left=path[0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        go_path.append(left)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        right=path[1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        while len(right)>0:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            left=right[0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            go_path.append(left)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            right=right[1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        go_path.reverse()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        for i in range(len(go_path)):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            go_path[i]=go_path[i]+1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return cost,go_path
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if __name__ == '__main__':
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    mtx_graph=[[0,1,inf,3,inf,inf,inf,inf,inf],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [1,0,5,inf,2,inf,inf,inf,inf],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [inf,inf,0,1,inf,6,inf,inf,inf],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [inf,inf,inf,0,inf,7,inf,9,inf],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [inf,2,3,inf,0,4,2,inf,8],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [inf,inf,6,7,inf,0,inf,2,inf],

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [inf,inf,inf,inf,inf,inf,1,0,2],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [inf,inf,inf,inf,8,inf,3,2,0]]

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    leght,path=Dijkstra(edges,1,9)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                inf=1E+12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def Floyd(graph):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    N=len(graph)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    A=np.array(graph)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    path=np.zeros((N,N))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for i in range(0,N):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        for j in range(0,N):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            if A[i][j]!=inf:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                path[i][j]=j
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for k in range(0,N):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        for i in range(0,N):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            for j in range(0,N):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if(A[i][k]+A[k][j]<A[i][j]):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    A[i][j]=A[i][k]+A[k][j]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    path[i][j]=path[i][k]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for i in range(0,N):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        for j in range(0,N):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            path[i][j]=path[i][j]+1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print('')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(A)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print('')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(path)
