                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import networkx as nx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def draw(g):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    pos = nx.spring_layout(g)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    labels = nx.get_edge_attributes(g, 'weight')  # YouCans, XUPT
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    nx.draw_networkx_edge_labels(g, pos, edge_labels=labels, font_color='red')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    nx.draw(g, pos,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            arrows=True,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            with_labels=True,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            nodelist=g.nodes(),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            style='dashed',
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            edge_color='b',
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            width=2,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            node_color='y',
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            alpha=0.5)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.show()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                g_data = [(1, 2, 1.3), (1, 3, 2.1), (1, 4, 0.9), (1, 5, 0.7), (1, 6, 1.8), (1, 7, 2.0), (1, 8, 1.8), (2, 3, 0.9),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          (2, 4, 1.8), (2, 5, 1.2), (2, 6, 2.8), (2, 7, 2.3), (2, 8, 1.1), (3, 4, 2.6), (3, 5, 1.7), (3, 6, 2.5),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          (3, 7, 1.9), (3, 8, 1.0), (4, 5, 0.7), (4, 6, 1.6), (4, 7, 1.5), (4, 8, 0.9), (5, 6, 0.9), (5, 7, 1.1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          (5, 8, 0.8), (6, 7, 0.6), (6, 8, 1.0), (7, 8, 0.5)]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                g = nx.Graph()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import networkx as nx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def prim(G, s):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dist = {}   # dist
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    parent = {} # parent
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Q = list(G.nodes()) # Q
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    MAXDIST = 9999.99    # MAXDIST
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # MAXDISTNone
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for v in G.nodes():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        dist[v] = MAXDIST
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        parent[v] = None
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # s0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    dist[s] = 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # Q
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # Q
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    while Q:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        # uu
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        u = Q[0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        for v in Q:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            if (dist[v] < dist[u]):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                u = v
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Q.remove(u)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        # u
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        for v in G.adj[u]:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            if (v in Q) and (G[u][v]['weight'] < dist[v]):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                parent[v] = u
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                dist[v] = G[u][v]['weight']
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for key,val in list(parent.items()):  #NoneNone
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if val==None:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            del parent[key]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return parent
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                g_data = [(1, 2, 1.3), (1, 3, 2.1), (1, 4, 0.9), (1, 5, 0.7), (1, 6, 1.8), (1, 7, 2.0), (1, 8, 1.8), (2, 3, 0.9),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          (2, 4, 1.8), (2, 5, 1.2), (2, 6, 2.8), (2, 7, 2.3), (2, 8, 1.1), (3, 4, 2.6), (3, 5, 1.7), (3, 6, 2.5),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          (3, 7, 1.9), (3, 8, 1.0), (4, 5, 0.7), (4, 6, 1.6), (4, 7, 1.5), (4, 8, 0.9), (5, 6, 0.9), (5, 7, 1.1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          (5, 8, 0.8), (6, 7, 0.6), (6, 8, 1.0), (7, 8, 0.5)]

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 2. Minimum Cost FlowMCF
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                G2 = nx.DiGraph()  #  DiGraph
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                G2.add_edges_from([('s','v1',{'capacity': 7, 'weight': 4}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('s','v2',{'capacity': 8, 'weight': 4}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v1','v3',{'capacity': 9, 'weight': 1}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v2','v1',{'capacity': 5, 'weight': 5}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v2','v4',{'capacity': 9, 'weight': 4}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v3','v4',{'capacity': 6, 'weight': 2}),

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeLabel2 = nx.get_edge_attributes(G2, 'weight')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeLabel = {}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in edgeLabel1.keys():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    edgeLabel[i] = f'({edgeLabel1[i]:},{edgeLabel2[i]:})'  # ()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ---
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                lenShortestPath = nx.shortest_path_length(G2, 's', 't', weight="weight")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                shortestPath = nx.shortest_path(G2, 's', 't', weight="weight")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # print("\n: ", shortestPath)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # print(": ", lenShortestPath)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ---
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                minCostmaxFlow = nx.max_flow_min_cost(G2, 's', 't')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                minCost = nx.cost_of_flow(G2, minCostmaxFlow)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                maxFlow = sum(minCostmaxFlow['s'][j] for j in minCostmaxFlow['s'].keys())  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("\n: {}".format(maxFlow))  #

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                v = 0

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v += 1  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    G2.add_node("s", demand=-v)  # nx.min_cost_flow() 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    G2.add_node("t", demand=v)  # /
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    try:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        # (demand=v)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        minFlowCost = nx.min_cost_flow_cost(G2)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        minFlowDict = nx.min_cost_flow(G2)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        # minFlowCost, minFlowDict = nx.network_simplex(G2)  # --
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print(": {:2d}\t:{}".format(v, minFlowCost))  # (demand=v)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        # print(": ", minFlowDict)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    except Exception as e:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print(": {:2d}\t".format(v))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print("\n v={:2d}({})".format(v, str(e)))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        break  #  while True 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeLists = []
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in minFlowDict.keys():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for j in minFlowDict[i].keys():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        edgeLabel[(i, j)] += ',f=' + str(minFlowDict[i][j])  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if minFlowDict[i][j] > 0:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            edgeLists.append((i, j))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                maxFlow = sum(minFlowDict['s'][j] for j in minFlowDict['s'].keys())  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("\n: {:2d},\t:{}".format(maxFlow, minFlowCost))  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(": ", minFlowDict)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("", edgeLists)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pos={'s':(0,5),'v1':(4,2),'v2':(4,8),'v3':(10,2),'v4':(10,8),'t':(14,5)}  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ax.text(6,2.5,"youcans-xupt",color='gainsboro')

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                3: nx.cost_of_flow() 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                4: maxFlow  s 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                5:  c w  f (13,7),f=11 13 7 11
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                6: edge_color=mwidth=2 0 f=0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                '''
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt #  Matplotlib 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import networkx as nx  #  NetworkX 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 3. Minimum Cost Maximum FlowMCMF
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                G3 = nx.DiGraph()  #  DiGraph
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                G3.add_edges_from([('s','v1',{'capacity': 13, 'weight': 7}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('s','v2',{'capacity': 9, 'weight': 9}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v1','v3',{'capacity': 6, 'weight': 6}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v1','v4',{'capacity': 5, 'weight': 5}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v2','v1',{'capacity': 4, 'weight': 4}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v2','v3',{'capacity': 5, 'weight': 2}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v2','v5',{'capacity': 5, 'weight': 5}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v3','v4',{'capacity': 5, 'weight': 2}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v3','v5',{'capacity': 4, 'weight': 1}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v3','t',{'capacity': 4, 'weight': 4}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v4','t', {'capacity': 9, 'weight': 7}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('v5','t',{'capacity': 9, 'weight': 5})]) #  'capacity', 'weight'
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                minCostFlow = nx.max_flow_min_cost(G3, 's', 't')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                minCost = nx.cost_of_flow(G3, minCostFlow)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                maxFlow = sum(minCostFlow['s'][j] for j in minCostFlow['s'].keys())  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeLabel1 = nx.get_edge_attributes(G3,'capacity')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeLabel2 = nx.get_edge_attributes(G3,'weight')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeLabel={}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in edgeLabel1.keys():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    edgeLabel[i]=f'({edgeLabel1[i]:},{edgeLabel2[i]:})'  # ()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeLists = []
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in minCostFlow.keys():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for j in minCostFlow[i].keys():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        edgeLabel[(i, j)] += ',f=' + str(minCostFlow[i][j])  #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if minCostFlow[i][j]>0:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            edgeLists.append((i,j))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(": ", minCostFlow)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("", edgeLists)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(": ", maxFlow)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(": ", minCost)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pos={'s':(0,5), 'v1':(3,9), 'v2':(3,1), 'v3':(6,5), 'v4':(9,9),'v5':(9,1), 't':(12,5)}  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.text(5,1.5,"youcans-xupt",color='gainsboro')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.set_title("Minimum Cost Maximum Flow with NetworkX")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw(G3,pos,with_labels=True,node_color='c',node_size=300,font_size=10)   # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edge_labels(G3,pos,edgeLabel,font_size=10)  # 'capacity','weight' + minCostFlow
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edges(G3,pos,edgelist=edgeLists,edge_color='m',width=2)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.axis('on')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('F1','W2',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 3}),  # W1~W2

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('W1','R1',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 2}),  # R1~R4
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('W1','R2',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 6}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('W1','R3',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 3}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('W1','R4',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 6}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('W2','R1',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 4}),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('W2','R2',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 4}),

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ('W2','R4',{'capacity': 9e5, 'weight': 5})]) #  'capacity', 'weight'

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pos={'F1':(2,6.5),'F2':(2,3.5),'W1':(5,6.5),'W2':(5,3.5),'R1':(9,8),'R2':(9,6),'R3':(9,4),'R4':(9,2)}  #

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            edgeLists.append((i, j))

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import pulp
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (1)  TransportCost: (LpMinimize)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP = pulp.LpProblem("TransportCostProblem", sense=pulp.LpMinimize)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (2)  f11~f22, w11~w24
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f11 = pulp.LpVariable('F1-W1', lowBound=0, upBound=600, cat='Continuous')  #  f11
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f12 = pulp.LpVariable('F1-W2', lowBound=0, upBound=600, cat='Continuous')  #  f12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f21 = pulp.LpVariable('F2-W1', lowBound=0, upBound=400, cat='Continuous')  #  f21
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f22 = pulp.LpVariable('F2-W2', lowBound=0, upBound=400, cat='Continuous')  #  f22
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w11 = pulp.LpVariable('W1-R1', lowBound=0, upBound=200, cat='Continuous')  #  w11
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w21 = pulp.LpVariable('W2-R1', lowBound=0, upBound=200, cat='Continuous')  #  w21
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w12 = pulp.LpVariable('W1-R2', lowBound=0, upBound=150, cat='Continuous')  #  w12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w22 = pulp.LpVariable('W2-R2', lowBound=0, upBound=150, cat='Continuous')  #  w22
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w13 = pulp.LpVariable('W1-R3', lowBound=0, upBound=350, cat='Continuous')  #  w13
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w23 = pulp.LpVariable('W2-R3', lowBound=0, upBound=350, cat='Continuous')  #  w23
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w14 = pulp.LpVariable('W1-R4', lowBound=0, upBound=300, cat='Continuous')  #  w14
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                w24 = pulp.LpVariable('W2-R4', lowBound=0, upBound=300, cat='Continuous')  #  w24
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (3)  cost
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (2*f11 + 3*f12 + 3*f21 +   f22 + 2*w11 + 6*w12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             +  3*w13 + 6*w14 + 4*w21 + 4*w22 + 6*w23 + 5*w24)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (4) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (f11 + f12 <= 600)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (f21 + f22 <= 400)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (w11 + w21 == 200)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (w12 + w22 == 150)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (w13 + w23 == 350)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (w14 + w24 == 300)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (f11 +f21 == w11 + w12 + w13 + w14)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP += (f12 +f22 == w21 + w22 + w23 + w24)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (5) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                transportLP.solve()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (6) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("2. PuLP ")  # PuLP 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(transportLP)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("Optimization result")  # PuLP 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for v in transportLP.variables():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(v.name, " = ", v.varValue)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("\n = ", pulp.value(transportLP.objective))  #

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Multi-Commodity Flow Prolem NP

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                v0 AB v6v5 AB 6.05.0

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                G G w 0
