                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                '''
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                1:  nx.DiGraph() G.add_weighted_edges_from()  (node1,node2,{capacity:c1, weight:w1})  capacity  weight capacity  weight 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                2: supplyAsupplyB  AB 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                3:  capacity  weight 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                4:  PuLP 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                (1) MCFproblem
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                (2) fAfB 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                step1: fAfB  AB  G2 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                step2: fAfB  0 pulp.LpVariable.dicts  upBound 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                step3:  fAfB  maxCapacity
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                step4: G2.edges()  G2  fAfB  AB  edges 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                {('v0', 'v1'): FlowA_('v0',_'v1'), ('v0', 'v2'): FlowA_('v0',_'v2'), ('v1', 'v3'): FlowA_('v1',_'v3'), ('v2', 'v1'): FlowA_('v2',_'v1'), ('v2', 'v4'): FlowA_('v2',_'v4'), ('v3', 'v4'): FlowA_('v3',_'v4'), ('v3', 'v5'): FlowA_('v3',_'v5'), ('v3', 'v6'): FlowA_('v3',_'v6'), ('v4', 'v1'): FlowA_('v4',_'v1'), ('v4', 'v5'): FlowA_('v4',_'v5'), ('v4', 'v6'): FlowA_('v4',_'v6')}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                {('v0', 'v1'): FlowB_('v0',_'v1'), ('v0', 'v2'): FlowB_('v0',_'v2'), ('v1', 'v3'): FlowB_('v1',_'v3'), ('v2', 'v1'): FlowB_('v2',_'v1'), ('v2', 'v4'): FlowB_('v2',_'v4'), ('v3', 'v4'): FlowB_('v3',_'v4'), ('v3', 'v5'): FlowB_('v3',_'v5'), ('v3', 'v6'): FlowB_('v3',_'v6'), ('v4', 'v1'): FlowB_('v4',_'v1'), ('v4', 'v5'): FlowB_('v4',_'v5'), ('v4', 'v6'): FlowB_('v4',_'v6')}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                (3)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 AB  edges  fAfB  weight
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                : 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                step1:  edgeWeight = nx.get_edge_attributes(G2, weight)  weight  for edge in G2.edges 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                step2:  KaTeX parse error: Undefined control sequence: \* at position 8: w(edge)\* [fA(edge)+fB(e  KaTeX parse error: Undefined control sequence: \* at position 9: wA(edge)\*fA(edge)+wB(edg 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                step3: MCFproblem += pulp.lpSum([edgeWeight[edge] * (fA[edge]+fB[edge]) for edge in G2.edges])  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                (4)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                1: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                2: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2.1:  for node in G2.nodes 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2.2: in_degree(node)  node  0 out_degree(node)  node  0 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2.3: in_edges(nbunch=node)  node out_edges(nbunch=node)  node 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2.4: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2.5: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2.6: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2.7: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v0, [('v0', 'v1'), ('v0', 'v2')]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v1, [('v0', 'v1'), ('v2', 'v1'), ('v4', 'v1')], [('v1', 'v3')]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v2, [('v0', 'v2')], [('v2', 'v1'), ('v2', 'v4')]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v3, [('v1', 'v3')], [('v3', 'v4'), ('v3', 'v5'), ('v3', 'v6')]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v4, [('v2', 'v4'), ('v3', 'v4')], [('v4', 'v1'), ('v4', 'v5'), ('v4', 'v6')]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v5, [('v3', 'v5'), ('v4', 'v5')]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    v6, [('v3', 'v6'), ('v4', 'v6')]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                (5)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                '''
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import pulp
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # PuLP  (Multi-commodity Flow Problem YouCans-XUPT)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeWeight = nx.get_edge_attributes(G2, 'weight')  # 'weight', 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgeCapacity = nx.get_edge_attributes(G2, 'capacity')  # 'capacity', 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                maxCapacity = max(edgeCapacity.values())  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(edgeWeight)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("max(Weight)",max(edgeWeight.values()))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("max(Capacity)",max(edgeCapacity.values()))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (1)  MCFproblem: (LpMinimize)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                MCFproblem = pulp.LpProblem("MultiCommodityFlowProb", sense=pulp.LpMinimize)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (2)  fA(edges), fB(edges)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # itemsG2 = ["A","B"]  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fA = pulp.LpVariable.dicts("FlowA", G2.edges(), lowBound=0.0, upBound=maxCapacity, cat='Continuous')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fB = pulp.LpVariable.dicts("FlowB", G2.edges(), lowBound=0.0, upBound=maxCapacity, cat='Continuous')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(fA)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(fB)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (3) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                MCFproblem += pulp.lpSum([edgeWeight[edge] * (fA[edge]+fB[edge]) for edge in G2.edges])  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (4) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for edge in G2.edges:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    MCFproblem += (fA[edge] + fB[edge] - edgeCapacity[edge] <= 0)  # edgeCapacity[edge], 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for node in G2.nodes:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if G2.in_degree(node) == 0:  #  0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print("{}, {}".format(node,G2.out_edges(nbunch=node)))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        MCFproblem += (sum(fA[edge] for edge in G2.out_edges(nbunch=node)) <= supplyA)  # A 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        MCFproblem += (sum(fB[edge] for edge in G2.out_edges(nbunch=node)) <= supplyB)  # B 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    elif G2.out_degree(node) == 0:  #  0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print("{}, {}".format(node,G2.in_edges(nbunch=node)))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if node=='v6':  # , v6  B
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            MCFproblem += (sum(fA[edge] for edge in G2.in_edges(nbunch=node)) == supplyA)  # A 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if node=='v5':  # , v5  A
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            MCFproblem += (sum(fB[edge] for edge in G2.in_edges(nbunch=node)) == supplyB)  # B 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    else:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print("{}, {}, {}".format(node,G2.in_edges(nbunch=node),G2.out_edges(nbunch=node)))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        MCFproblem += (sum(fA[edge1] for edge1 in G2.out_edges(nbunch=node))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       - sum(fA[edge2] for edge2 in G2.in_edges(nbunch=node)) == 0)  #  = 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        MCFproblem += (sum(fB[edge1] for edge1 in G2.out_edges(nbunch=node))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       - sum(fB[edge2] for edge2 in G2.in_edges(nbunch=node)) == 0)  #  = 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (5) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                MCFproblem.solve()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # (6) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("2. PuLP ")  # PuLP 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(MCFproblem)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("Optimization result")  # PuLP 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for v in MCFproblem.variables():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(v.name, " = ", v.varValue)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("\n = ", pulp.value(MCFproblem.objective))  #

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • ESEarliest Start ES = max{EF(preceding activities)}

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • EFEarliest FinishEF = ES+DU DU

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • LFLatest Finish LF = min{LS(successor activities)}

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • LSLatest StartLS = LF -DUDU

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • TFTotal float timeTF = LF - EF

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • FFFree float timeFF = min{ES(successor activities)} - EF

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                AOV AOEAOV AOE

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 1. (topological sequence)  (critical path)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # Activity on edge network(AOE), 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                DG = nx.DiGraph()  #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                DG.add_weighted_edges_from([(1, 2, 5), (1, 3, 10), (1, 4, 11),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (2, 5, 4),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (3, 4, 4), (3, 5, 0),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (4, 6, 15),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (5, 6, 21), (5, 7, 25), (5, 8, 35),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (6, 7, 0), (6, 8, 20),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (7, 8, 15)])  # : (n1,n2,weight)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                lenNodes = len(DG.nodes)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                topoSeq = list(nx.topological_sort(DG))  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nodeCP = list(nx.dag_longest_path(DG))  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                lenCP = nx.dag_longest_path_length(DG)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgesCP=[]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for k in range(1,len(nodeCP)):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    edgesCP.append((nodeCP[k-1],nodeCP[k]))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("{}".format(topoSeq))  # [1, 3, 4, 2, 5, 6, 7, 8]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("{}".format(nodeCP))  # [1, 3, 5, 6, 8]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("{}".format(edgesCP))  # [(1, 3), (3, 5), (5, 6), (6, 8)]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("{}".format(lenCP))  # 51
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pos = {1:(0,4), 2:(5,7), 3:(5,4), 4:(5,1), 5:(10,7), 6:(10,1), 7:(15,4), 8:(20,4)}  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgesDG = DG.edges
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgesDashed = [(3,5),(6,7)]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgesSolid = list(set(edgesDG)-set(edgesDashed))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                labels = nx.get_edge_attributes(DG, 'weight')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # nx.draw(DG, pos, with_labels=True, node_color='skyblue')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_nodes(DG, pos, node_color='orange',node_size=400)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_labels(DG, pos)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edges(DG, pos, edgelist=edgesSolid, edge_color='dimgrey', style='solid')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edges(DG, pos, edgelist=edgesDashed, edge_color='grey', style='dashed')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edge_labels(DG, pos, edge_labels=labels, font_color='dimgrey')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.set_title("Project network graph by youcans@xupt")

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt  #  Matplotlib 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import networkx as nx  #  NetworkX 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 2. (critical path method)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                DG = nx.DiGraph()  #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # Activity on edge network(AOE), 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                DG.add_nodes_from(range(1, 8), VE=0, VL=0)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                DG.add_weighted_edges_from([(1, 2, 5), (1, 3, 10), (1, 4, 11),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (2, 5, 4),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (3, 4, 4), (3, 5, 0),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (4, 6, 15),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (5, 6, 21), (5, 7, 25), (5, 8, 35),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (6, 7, 0), (6, 8, 20),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            (7, 8, 15)])  # : (node1,node2,weight)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                lenNodes = len(DG.nodes)  #  YouCans
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                topoSeq = list(nx.topological_sort(DG))  # : [1, 3, 4, 2, 5, 7, 6, 8]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ---  VE ---
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                VE = [0 for i in range(lenNodes)]  #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in range(lenNodes):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for e in DG.in_edges(topoSeq[i]):  #  topoSeq[i]  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        VEij = DG.nodes[e[0]]["VE"] + DG[e[0]][e[1]]["weight"]  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if VEij > VE[i]: VE[i] = VEij  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    DG.add_node(topoSeq[i], VE=VE[i])  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ---  VL ---
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                revSeq = list(reversed(topoSeq))  #  VL
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                VL = [DG.nodes[revSeq[0]]["VE"] for i in range(lenNodes)]  #   VE 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for i in range(lenNodes):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for e in DG.out_edges(revSeq[i]):  #  revSeq[i]  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        VLij = DG.nodes[e[1]]["VL"] - DG[e[0]][e[1]]["weight"]  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if VLij < VL[i]: VL[i] = VLij  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    DG.add_node(revSeq[i], VL=VL[i])  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("\n VE,  VL:")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for n in DG.nodes:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print("\t {}:\tVE= {}\tVL= {}".format(n, DG.nodes[n]["VE"], DG.nodes[n]["VL"]))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # ---  ES, LS ---
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                cpDG = nx.DiGraph()  # , 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("\n ES,  LS:")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                for e in DG.edges:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    DG[e[0]][e[1]]["ES"] = DG.nodes[e[0]]["VE"]  #  VE
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # Wij = DG[e[0]][e[1]]['weight']
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    DG[e[0]][e[1]]["LS"] = DG.nodes[e[1]]["VL"] - DG[e[0]][e[1]]["weight"]  #  VL 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if DG[e[0]][e[1]]["ES"] == DG[e[0]][e[1]]["LS"]:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        cpDG.add_edge(e[0], e[1], weight=DG[e[0]][e[1]]["weight"])  #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # print("\t {}:\tES= {}\tLS= {}".format(e, DG[e[0]][e[1]]["ES"], DG[e[0]][e[1]]["LS"]))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print("\t {}:\tES= {}\tLS= {}\tDU= {}".format(e, DG[e[0]][e[1]]["ES"], DG[e[0]][e[1]]["LS"], DG[e[0]][e[1]]["weight"]))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                lenCP = sum(cpDG[e[0]][e[1]]["weight"] for e in cpDG.edges)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print("\n:{}".format(cpDG.edges))  # YouCans, XUPT
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(":{}".format(lenCP))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pos = {1:(0,4), 2:(5,7), 3:(5,4), 4:(5,1), 5:(10,7), 6:(10,1), 7:(15,4), 8:(20,4)}  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgesDG = DG.edges
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgesDashed = [(3,5),(6,7)]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                edgesSolid = list(set(edgesDG)-set(edgesDashed))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                labels = nx.get_edge_attributes(DG, "weight") 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_nodes(DG, pos, node_color='orange',node_size=400)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_labels(DG, pos)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edges(DG, pos, edgelist=edgesSolid, edge_color='dimgrey', style='solid')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edges(DG, pos, edgelist=edgesDashed, edge_color='grey', style='dashed')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edge_labels(DG, pos, edge_labels=labels, font_color='dimgrey')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                nx.draw_networkx_edges(DG, pos, edgelist=cpDG.edges, edge_color='r', width=2)  # : 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ax.set_title("Project network graph by youcans@xupt")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.xlim(-2, 22)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.ylim(-1, 9)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.axis('on')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                si.interp1d(x,y,kind='str')

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • xy xy

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • kind(linear,zero,slinear,quadratic,cubic)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import scipy.interpolate as si
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x=np.linspace(-np.pi,np.pi,20)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                y=np.sin(x)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xnew=np.linspace(-np.pi/2,np.pi,300)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f1=si.interp1d(x,y,kind='linear')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f2=si.interp1d(x,y,kind='zero')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f3=si.interp1d(x,y,kind='slinear')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f4=si.interp1d(x,y,kind='quadratic')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                f5=si.interp1d(x,y,kind='cubic')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.figure()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.title("Data Interpolate")
