                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                R1R

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xxxxxxxxxx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def __sst(y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SST(total sum of squares) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_predicted: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: SST
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y_mean = sum(y_no_fitting) / len(y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    s_list =[(y - y_mean)**2 for y in y_no_fitting]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    sst = sum(s_list)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return sst
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def __ssr(y_fitting, y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SSR(regression sum of squares) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_fitting: List[int] or array[int]  y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: SSR
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y_mean = sum(y_no_fitting) / len(y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    s_list =[(y - y_mean)**2 for y in y_fitting]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ssr = sum(s_list)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return ssr
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def __sse(y_fitting, y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SSE(error sum of squares) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: SSE
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    s_list = [(y_fitting[i] - y_no_fitting[i])**2 for i in range(len(y_fitting))]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    sse = sum(s_list)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return sse
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def goodness_of_fit(y_fitting, y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    R^2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: R^2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SSR = __ssr(y_fitting, y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SST = __sst(y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    rr = SSR /SST
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return rr

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from scipy.optimize import leastsq
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def __sst(y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SST(total sum of squares) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_predicted: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: SST
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y_mean = sum(y_no_fitting) / len(y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    s_list =[(y - y_mean)**2 for y in y_no_fitting]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    sst = sum(s_list)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return sst
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def __ssr(y_fitting, y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SSR(regression sum of squares) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_fitting: List[int] or array[int]  y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: SSR
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    y_mean = sum(y_no_fitting) / len(y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    s_list =[(y - y_mean)**2 for y in y_fitting]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ssr = sum(s_list)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return ssr
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def __sse(y_fitting, y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SSE(error sum of squares) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: SSE
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    s_list = [(y_fitting[i] - y_no_fitting[i])**2 for i in range(len(y_fitting))]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    sse = sum(s_list)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return sse
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def goodness_of_fit(y_fitting, y_no_fitting):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    R^2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y_no_fitting: List[int] or array[int] y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: R^2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SSR = __ssr(y_fitting, y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    SST = __sst(y_no_fitting)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    rr = SSR /SST
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return rr
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x = [4, 8, 10, 12, 25, 32, 43, 58, 63, 69, 79]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                y = [20, 33, 50, 56, 42, 31, 33, 46, 65, 75, 78]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                x_arr = np.array(x)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                y_arr = np.array(y)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def fitting_func(p, x):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param p: array[int] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param x: array[int] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: array[int] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    f = np.poly1d(p)    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return f(x)         # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def error_func(p, x, y):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param p: array[int] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param x: array[int] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param y: array[int] ()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    err = fitting_func(p, x) - y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return err
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def n_poly(n, x, y):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    n 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :param n: ()n=32
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    :return: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    """
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    p_init = np.random.randn(n+1)   #  n
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    parameters = leastsq(error_func, p_init, args=(np.array(x), np.array(y)))    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return parameters[0]    # leastsq[wn...w2w1w0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                para_1 = n_poly(1, x_arr, y_arr)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(":", para_1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(":", np.poly1d(para_1))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(":", fitting_func(para_1, x_arr))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                print(":", goodness_of_fit(fitting_func(para_1, x_arr), y_arr))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                para_2 = n_poly(2, x_arr, y_arr)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                para_3 = n_poly(3, x_arr, y_arr)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                para_4 = n_poly(4, x_arr, y_arr)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                para_5 = n_poly(5, x_arr, y_arr)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                figure2 = plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(x_arr, fitting_func(para_1, x_arr), color="#72CD28", label='')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(x_arr, fitting_func(para_2, x_arr), color="#EBBD43", label='')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(x_arr, fitting_func(para_3, x_arr), color="#50BFFB", label='')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(x_arr, fitting_func(para_4, x_arr), color="gold", label='')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.plot(x_arr, fitting_func(para_5, x_arr), color="#13EAC9", label='')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.scatter(x_arr, y_arr, color='#50BFFB', marker="p", label='')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.title("leastsq", fontsize=13)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.xlabel('x', fontsize=13)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.ylabel('y', fontsize=13)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.legend(loc=4, fontsize=11)    # legend
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                plt.show()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Regression analysis)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xxxxxxxxxx
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import statsmodels.api as sm
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from statsmodels.sandbox.regression.predstd import wls_prediction_std
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def main(): 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    nSample = 100
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x1 = np.linspace(0, 10, nSample)  #  0 10 nSample
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    e = np.random.normal(size=len(x1))  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yTrue = 2.36 + 1.58 * x1  #  y = b0 + b1*x1   normal
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yTest = yTrue + e  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # (OLS)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    X = sm.add_constant(x1)  #  X x0=[1,...1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    model = sm.OLS(yTest, X)  # OLS
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    results = model.fit()  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yFit = results.fittedvalues  #  y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    prstd, ivLow, ivUp = wls_prediction_std(results) # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # OLS model: Y = b0 + b1*X + e
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(results.summary())  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print("\nOLS model: Y = b0 + b1 * x")  # b0: b1: 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print('Parameters: ', results.params)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, yTest, 'o', label="data")  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, yFit, 'r-', label="OLS")  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, ivUp, '--',color='orange',label="upConf")  # 95%  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, ivLow, '--',color='orange',label="lowConf")  # 95%  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.legend(loc='best')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.title('OLS linear regression ')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.show()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if __name__ == '__main__':
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    main()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import statsmodels.api as sm
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                from statsmodels.sandbox.regression.predstd import wls_prediction_std
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def main():  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    nSample = 100
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x0 = np.ones(nSample)  #  x0=[1,...1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x1 = np.linspace(0, 20, nSample)  #  0 10 nSample
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x2 = np.sin(x1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    x3 = (x1 - 5) ** 2
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    X = np.column_stack((x0, x1, x2, x3))  # (nSample,4): [x0,x1,x2,...,xm]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    beta = [5., 0.5, 0.5, -0.02]  # beta = [b1,b2,...,bm]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yTrue = np.dot(X, beta)  #  y = b1*x1 + ...+ bm*xm
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yTest = yTrue + 0.5 * np.random.normal(size=nSample)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # (OLS)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    model = sm.OLS(yTest, X)  #  OLS : Y = b0 + b1*X + ... + bm*Xm + e
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    results = model.fit()  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yFit = results.fittedvalues  #  y
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print(results.summary())  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print("\nOLS model: Y = b0 + b1*X + ... + bm*Xm")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    print('Parameters: ', results.params)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    prstd, ivLow, ivUp = wls_prediction_std(results)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, yTest, 'o', label="data")  # +
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, yTrue, 'b-', label="True")  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, yFit, 'r-', label="OLS")  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, ivUp, '--', color='orange', label="ConfInt")  #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.plot(x1, ivLow, '--', color='orange')  #  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ax.legend(loc='best')  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.xlabel('x')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.ylabel('y')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    plt.show()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if __name__ == '__main__':
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    main()
