                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            totalMar += 1  #  Markov
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            # ---
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            #  [min,max] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            #  1 n n-1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            xNew[:] = xNow[:]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            v = random.randint(0, nVar - 1)  #  [0,nVar-1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            if(not integer):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xNew[v] = xNow[v] + scale * (xMax[v] - xMin[v]) * random.normalvariate(0, 1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            else:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xNew[v] = round(xNow[v] + scale * (xMax[v]-xMin[v]) * random.normalvariate(0, 1)) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            # random.normalvariate(0, 1)0 1 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            xNew[v] = max(min(xNew[v], xMax[v]), xMin[v])  #  [min,max] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            # ---
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            #  func 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            fxNew = func(xNew, nVar, kIter)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            deltaE = fxNew - yNow
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            # --- Metropolis 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            #  Metropolis 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            if fxNew < yNow:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                accept = True
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                kBetter += 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            else:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                pAccept = math.exp(-deltaE / tNow)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if pAccept > random.random():
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    accept = True  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    kBadAccept += 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                else:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    accept = False  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    kBadRefuse += 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            if accept == True:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                xNow[:] = xNew[:]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                yNow = fxNew
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                if fxNew < yBest:  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    yBest = fxNew
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    xBest[:] = xNew[:]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    totalImprove += 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    scale = scale * 0.99  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        pBadAccept = kBadAccept / (kBadAccept + kBadRefuse)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        recordIter.append(kIter)  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        recordyNow.append(round(yNow, 4))  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        recordyBest.append(round(yBest, 4))  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        recordPBad.append(round(pBadAccept, 4))  # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        tNow = tNow * alfa
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        kIter = kIter + 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        yBest = func(xBest, nVar, kIter)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return xBest,yBest,yNow,kIter,recordyNow,recordyBest

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                t=np.argwhere(w[0]==tzz) #

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def dataDirection_2(datas, x_min, x_max):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    def normalization(data):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if data <= x_min or data >= x_max:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data > x_min and data < (x_min + x_max) / 2:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 2 * (data - x_min) / (x_max - x_min)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data < x_max and data >= (x_min + x_max) / 2:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 2 * (x_max - data) / (x_max - x_min)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return list(map(normalization, datas))

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def dataDirection_3(datas, x_min, x_max, x_minimum, x_maximum):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    def normalization(data):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if data >= x_min and data <= x_max:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data <= x_minimum or data >= x_maximum:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data > x_max and data < x_maximum:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 1 - (data - x_max) / (x_maximum - x_max)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data < x_min and data > x_minimum:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 1 - (x_min - data) / (x_min - x_minimum)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return list(map(normalization, datas))

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import pandas as pd
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def topsis(data, weight=None):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    data = data / np.sqrt((data ** 2).sum())
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Z = pd.DataFrame([data.min(), data.max()], index=['', ''])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    weight = entropyWeight(data) if weight is None else np.array(weight)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Result = data.copy()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Result[''] = np.sqrt(((data - Z.loc['']) ** 2 * weight).sum(axis=1))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Result[''] = np.sqrt(((data - Z.loc['']) ** 2 * weight).sum(axis=1))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Result[''] = Result[''] / (Result[''] + Result[''])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Result[''] = Result.rank(ascending=False)['']
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return Result, Z, weight

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import pandas as pd
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def dataDirection_3(datas, x_min, x_max, x_minimum, x_maximum):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    def normalization(data):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if data >= x_min and data <= x_max:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data <= x_minimum or data >= x_maximum:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 0
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data > x_max and data < x_maximum:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 1 - (data - x_max) / (x_maximum - x_max)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif data < x_min and data > x_minimum:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            return 1 - (x_min - data) / (x_min - x_minimum)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return list(map(normalization, datas))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def dataDirection_1(datas, offset=0):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    def normalization(data):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        return 1 / (data + offset)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return list(map(normalization, datas))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                data = pd.DataFrame(
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    {'': [0.1, 0.2, 0.4, 0.9, 1.2], '': [5, 6, 7, 10, 2], '': [5000, 6000, 7000, 10000, 400],
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     '': [4.7, 5.6, 6.7, 2.3, 1.8]}, index=['' + i for i in list('ABCDE')])

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        {'': [0.1, 0.2, 0.4, 0.9, 1.2], '': [5, 6, 7, 10, 2], '': [5000, 6000, 7000, 10000, 400],

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def entropyWeight(data):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    data = np.array(data)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    P = data / data.sum(axis=0)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    E = np.nansum(-P * np.log(P) / np.log(len(data)), axis=0)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return (1 - E) / (1 - E).sum()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                entropyWeight(data)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                RI = {1: 0, 2: 0, 3: 0.58, 4: 0.90, 5: 1.12, 6: 1.24, 7: 1.32, 8: 1.41, 9: 1.45, 10: 1.49, 11: 1.51}
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def AHP(data):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    data = np.array(data)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    m = len(data)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    weight = (data / data.sum(axis=0)).sum(axis=1) / m
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Lambda = sum((weight * data).sum(axis=1) / (m * weight))
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    CI = (Lambda - m) / (m - 1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    CR = CI / RI[m]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if CR < 0.1:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print(f'lambda = {Lambda}')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print(f'weight = {weight}')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print(f'\nCI = {round(CI,2)}, RI = {RI[m]} \nCR = CI/RI = {round(CR,2)} < 0.1')
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        return weight
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    else:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        print(f'\nCI = {round(CI,2)}, RI = {RI[m]} \nCR = CI/RI = {round(CR,2)} >= 0.1')

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # gaincost,level_GRA
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    '''
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    df : dataframe
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    normaliza ["initial","mean"] 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    level None 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "gain"(),"cost"()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            dataframelevel="level""level"10
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    r  [0-1]   
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             0.5
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    '''
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def GRA(df,normaliza="initial",level=None,r=0.5):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if not isinstance(df,pd.DataFrame):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        df = pd.DataFrame(df)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if (normaliza not in ["initial","mean"]) or (r<0 or r>1):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        raise KeyError("")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    if level == "gain" or level == None:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        df_ = gain(df,normaliza)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        #
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    elif level == "cost":
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        df_ = cost(df,normaliza)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    else:# 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        try:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            df.columns.get_loc(level) # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        except:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            raise KeyError("")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        df_ = level_(df,normaliza,level)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        df_.drop(level,axis=1,inplace=True)# level
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    df_ = np.abs(df_ - df_.iloc[0,:]) # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    global_max = df_.max().max()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    global_min = df_.min().min()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    df_r = (global_min + r*global_max)/(df_ + r*global_max) # 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return df_r.mean(axis=1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # gain
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def gain(df,normaliza):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for i in range(df.shape[0]):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if normaliza == "initial" or normaliza==None:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            df.iloc[i] = df.iloc[i]/df.iloc[i,0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif normaliza == "mean":
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            df.iloc[i] = df.iloc[i]/df.mean(axis=1)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return df
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # cost
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def cost(df,normaliza):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    for i in range(df.shape[0]):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        if normaliza == "initial" or normaliza==None:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            df.iloc[i] = df.iloc[i,0]/df.iloc[i]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        elif normaliza == "mean":
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            df.iloc[i] = df.mean(axis=1)/df.iloc[i]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return df
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                # 0-1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def level_(df,normaliza,level):
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    # 10
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    df_gain = df[df[level]==1]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    df_cost = df[df[level]==0]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    df_1 = gain(df_gain,normaliza)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    df_2 = cost(df_cost,normaliza)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    return df_1.append(df_2)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import numpy as np
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import pandas as pd
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
